INSTALL
=========
1. Do run: composer install
2. To run tests: ./phpunit
3. To run script: php index.php

Information
===========
- To add a new type of tranportation, add a class that extends Vehicle. Just like the Train/Bus/Plane classes.

- Need more info, just give me a shout, so I can explain why I did things in a certain way - or why I did not.
